    "description": "<strong>《来者》是一款RPG合作冒险游戏。在游戏中，与团队合作，净化已被污染的星球，生存和发展下去。</strong> 赛宁人是强大而坚韧的一族，曾是热爱和平的太空战士和探险家。他们的星球遭受毁灭性灾害，一族面临灭绝危机，只能把最后的希望寄托在所剩无几的生还者。生还者在休眠舱内休眠，乘坐飞船逃离家园，希望能发现新的家园。<br><br>若干年后，赫尔曼号飞船发现了一颗合适的星球。于是，任务开始了：净化已被污染的索拉勒斯星，建造新家园。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/1a83db073a44c5d54fd470bad863e889.poster.avif?t=1702932877\" width=620 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/1a83db073a44c5d54fd470bad863e889.webm?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/1a83db073a44c5d54fd470bad863e889.mp4?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>然而，这颗星球上已已有原住民——托列克人，他们在索拉勒斯恶劣的环境中生存了下来。<br><br>托列克星人和赛宁星人通过合作，净化索拉勒斯，建立起深厚的友谊。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/c73f1b5f6e375e83627734b066a74f44.poster.avif?t=1702932877\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/c73f1b5f6e375e83627734b066a74f44.webm?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/c73f1b5f6e375e83627734b066a74f44.mp4?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>作为赛宁星人，你可以利用不同的塑造者和能量，以自己的方式在索拉勒斯生存下来。探索这个星球，找到合适的战衣来实施净化行动。<br><br>找出破坏索拉勒斯的幕后黑手！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/273dfe222b3005a0f4f81d2742f0874e.poster.avif?t=1702932877\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/273dfe222b3005a0f4f81d2742f0874e.webm?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/273dfe222b3005a0f4f81d2742f0874e.mp4?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>使用不同的能量塑造者，选择自己的风格： 艾瑞、以太、菲瑞和联合者。<br></strong></li><li><strong>探索和寻找不同的战衣，净化索拉勒斯，建立新家园。 <br></strong></li><li><strong>净化星球，获取资源，迎接最后的挑战。<br></strong></li><li><strong>支持单人和多人模式，迎接各种挑战，阻止宾诺克的最终实验。<br></strong></li><li><strong>支持竞技对战模式，在 PVP 竞技场与朋友对战，合理运用 4 种能量对抗其他玩家。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/21ac2fa74f6a80578d39d98621066208.poster.avif?t=1702932877\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/21ac2fa74f6a80578d39d98621066208.webm?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/21ac2fa74f6a80578d39d98621066208.mp4?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/5e4f49ac9a301a33d179b8f63fd8a3ac.poster.avif?t=1702932877\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/5e4f49ac9a301a33d179b8f63fd8a3ac.webm?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708570/extras/5e4f49ac9a301a33d179b8f63fd8a3ac.mp4?t=1702932877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></li></ul>",
